Name: YBit
About the game: YBit is a pixelated platformer adventure. About the Game You will be playing as a small hero made of information, trying to escape from a program that has crashed. Avoiding errors, not falling down and getting to the exits will be your mission. 100 levels Pixel art A background story 16 different types of platforms Full keyboard and joystick support How to Play Just move around with the arrows and press space to talk.
